race.description: Bella Group Services Provincial Maiden Handicap
race.comment: COLD MIST (10) deep into the prep today and finds his race with the sharp weight drop. Went back from the wide gate when a plugging fourth over 1300m at Kembla Grange. Can race a little closer from the gate and set to break through. CATHEDRAL COVE (9) drops in trip after failing to run the 1500m out when fifth at Kembla Grange. Placed at this trip three-back at Beaumont (Newcastle). In peak condition and capable of taking a hand in the finish. FUNSHOW (1) progressive gelding who gets a better set up at his third race start. Shouldered the 59kg when a tenacious second over 1200m at Gosford. No excuses today. ALL STAR (2) encouraging effort again when he stalked the speed from the wide gate to secure third over 1200m at Gosford. Has the speed to get across from the wide barrier. Place best. OAKFIELD UNIVERSE (4) no surprise to see her shed her Maiden tag third-up over this trip. Caught the eye at Gosford and gets map favours today.
